name: Moose men’s Chap Slim fit polo Shirt – Alloy
description:
Snazzy and Hip! Cool to the Core! Fashionable and Funky! Moose Men’s Polo T-shirts are out, a wide variety of your favorite colors/prints to choose from for your casual or semi-formal needs!

Fabric composition: 100% Cotton
Fabric pattern: Computer Jacquard
Fit type: Slim
Length: Regular
Wash care instructions: Machine wash
Add on features: Button with front placket, EMB logo, Moose neck tape at neck circumference and slit open at bottom, Special chambray fabric used for back patch. Flat knit collar.
